I have another search request for the Maxwell case, please. If there's any way to get these searches run before you're off 
tomorrow, I'd be very grateful.

"NYC024328", "NYC024349", and "NYC024350" in the "US v Epstein (SW Returns)" database on Relativity: 
•  Please run the search terms listed in the attached Word document entitled "Epstein Responsiveness Search Terms". 
Please tag all hits with a tag entitled "Potentially Responsive". I believe you modified these search terms when 
running them on a larger data set in the same database. Please feel free to use those modified terms on this 
search as well if that is easier. 
•  For all of the email addresses listed in the attached Word document entitled "Epstein Responsiveness Email 
Addresses," please pull any email with any of those addresses in the header (TO, FROM, CC, or 8CC). Please tag all 
of those emails with the same tag entitled "Potentially Responsive". 
Please let me know when these searches are complete, so that I can review the Potentially Responsive hits. Once we have 
reviewed, we will let you know what should be produced from that database. 
Thanks very much, 
(USANYS) <
